OL,3,CStation gets into World Cup spirit
OL,4,Cahead of England's historic semi-final
OL,6,FA railway station has embraced the
OL,7,FWorld Cup spirit as the nation gears
OL,8,Fup for England's historic semi-final
OL,9,Fclash against Argentina.
OL,11,FPassengers travelling through Holmes
OL,12,FChapel, Cheshire, spotted the new
OL,13,Fsignage on the platforms as the Three
OL,14,FLions prepare to take on the South
OL,15,FAmerican team at 8pm on Wednesday, 15
OL,16,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
