OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784191682
OL,3,CStation gets into World Cup spirit
OL,4,Cahead of England's historic semi-final
OL,6,FNorthern Rail has temporarily
OL,7,Frebranded the stop as "It's Coming
OL,8,FHolmes Chapel", with staff at the
OL,9,Fstation already getting into the
OL,10,Fspirit of things ahead of what
OL,11,Fpromises to be a action-packed night
OL,12,Ffor football fans.
OL,14,FThe name change is part of a push by
OL,15,Fthe train operator to get fans in the
OL,16,Fmood - and encourage them to leave the
OL,17,Fcar keys at home if they are heading
OL,18,Fout to watch the game.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784191682
OL,3,CStation gets into World Cup spirit
OL,4,Cahead of England's historic semi-final
OL,6,FAlex Hornby, Commercial and Customer
OL,7,FDirector for Northern, said the
OL,8,Foperator wanted to bring a bit of joy
OL,9,Fto the daily commute: "It's coming
OL,10,FHolmes Chapel!
OL,12,F"With England taking on Argentina in
OL,13,Fthe semi-final, we wanted to give our
OL,14,Fcustomers something to smile about on
OL,15,Fthe way to wherever they're watching
OL,16,Fthe game.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784191682
OL,3,CStation gets into World Cup spirit
OL,4,Cahead of England's historic semi-final
OL,6,F"On a more serious note, we're
OL,7,Fencouraging as many fans as possible
OL,8,Fto leave the car at home and travel by
OL,9,Ftrain, whether that's heading into
OL,10,Ftown for the atmosphere or just
OL,11,Fgetting home safely after full time."
OL,13,FWith the match expected to draw
OL,14,Fmassive crowds to pubs, town centres,
OL,15,Fand fan zones, Northern has confirmed
OL,16,Fthey will have trains running late
OL,17,Finto the evening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
